{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "本章揭示刘桥真实身份是萧佛狸。纽玉枢挟持刘桥企图突围，顾曲周出手解救，但萧佛狸突然发难，萧笑、贝玄衣同时攻击顾曲周。顾曲周在混战中被萧佛狸暗算，临死前才知真相。纽玉枢和廖碎也在混战中死亡。萧佛狸展现了无敌杀手的冷酷与实力，顾曲周壮烈牺牲。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "萧笑",
      "listener": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "text": "纽玉枢，你也无名得太久了。",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "speaker_name": "纽玉枢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao",
      "text": "是啊，所以我要做点出名的事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "顾曲周",
      "listener": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "text": "出名的方法，有很多种，这样并不好。",
      "tone": "劝诫",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "speaker_name": "纽玉枢",
      "listener": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "text": "这样很好。",
      "tone": "固执",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "speaker_name": "纽玉枢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样他可以带我平安出去。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bei_xuan_yi",
      "speaker_name": "贝玄衣",
      "listener": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "text": "放下刘大人，我们放你一条生路！",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "speaker_name": "纽玉枢",
      "listener": "char_bei_xuan_yi",
      "text": "你忘了，这里我是赢家，",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "speaker_name": "纽玉枢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赢家才有权说话。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_xiao_qing",
      "speaker_name": "水小情",
      "listener": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "text": "你——你是魏忠贤派来的人？！",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "speaker_name": "纽玉枢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在刘大人性命在我手中，我要离开，只要你们之中任何一人要动手，或者跟踪，我都会杀了刘桥，你们懂不懂？",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "speaker_name": "纽玉枢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们让不让路？！要不要他死？！",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "顾曲周",
      "listener": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "text": "我们不能放你。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "顾曲周",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刘大人落在你们手里，生不如死，我放你走，等于害了他，而且，",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "顾曲周",
      "listener": "char_niu_yu_shu",
      "text": "你手臂运力箍死刘大人前，我们还来得及出手；如果你用刀。你的刀根本杀不死人",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "顾曲周",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fo_li",
      "text": "我早该想到，他们……要杀的不是你……是我。",
      "tone": "悔恨",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fo_li",
      "speaker_name": "萧佛狸",
      "listener": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "text": "不能怪你。因为你不知道我就是萧佛狸。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "顾曲周",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fo_li",
      "text": "那我死在你手上，也算不冤……萧佛狸本来排名一直在我之上的。",
      "tone": "认命",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fo_li",
      "speaker_name": "萧佛狸",
      "listener": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "text": "我的排名一直都是在你之上。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "顾曲周",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fo_li",
      "text": "但你当杀手的品行，却远在我之下。",
      "tone": "鄙视",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fo_li",
      "speaker_name": "萧佛狸",
      "listener": "char_gu_qu_zhou",
      "text": "一个杀手若要无敌，是不能有人格的，所以我是‘无敌杀手’。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fo_li",
      "speaker_name": "萧佛狸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好刀！",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line": 117
    }
  ],
